== Overview ==  

* The kanji '''庚''' is a {{ill|pictogram|ja|象形文字|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} representing a type of musical instrument.<ref>{{Citation| author=Ji Xusheng (季旭昇)| year=2014| title=説文新証| location=Taipei| publisher=芸文印書館| isbn=978-957-520-168-5| page=965}}</ref><ref>{{Citation| author=Lin Zhiqiang et al. (林志強等)| year=2017| title=《文源》評注| location=Beijing| publisher=中国社会科学出版社| isbn=978-7-5203-0419-1| page=97}}</ref><ref>{{Citation| author=Ge Liang (葛亮)| year=2022| title=漢字再発現――従旧識到新知| location=Shanghai| publisher=上海書画出版社| isbn=978-7-5479-2884-4| pages=106–9}}</ref> The use of this character to represent the seventh stem is due to {{ill|phonetic loan|ja|仮借|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
